<view class="a"><uni-grid vue-id="1" column="{{column_num}}" show-border="{{true}}" square="{{true}}" data-event-opts="{{[['^change',[['change']]]]}}" bind:change="__e" bind:__l="__l" vue-slots="{{['default']}}"><block wx:for="{{list}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:for-index="index" wx:key="index"><uni-grid-item vue-id="{{('2-'+index)+','+('1')}}" data-n="item" c_index="{{item}}" highlight="{{a}}" bind:__l="__l" vue-slots="{{['default']}}"><text class="text">{{item}}</text></uni-grid-item></block></uni-grid><view class="time">用时:<text>{{time}}</text>秒</view><text class="click">{{"请点击:"+(nextNum+1)}}</text><view class="btns"><image src="../../static/images/sx.png" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['again',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e"></image><image src="../../static/images/sdf.png" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['random_sort',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e"></image></view><view hidden="{{!(istip)}}" class="maker"><image class="mak_bg" src="../../static/images/bgm.png"></image><image class="close" src="../../static/images/close.png" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['close',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e"></image><view class="center"><image class="game" src="../../static/images/game.png"></image><view class="kuang"><text>用手指按照1，2，3，4.......的顺序点击相应的方格,并口说数字,用时越少说明你越优秀呦!</text></view><image class="go" src="../../static/images/go.png" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['close',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e"></image><text data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['n_remind',['$event']]]]]}}" class="not" bindtap="__e">不再提醒</text></view></view></view>